Class AgencyParameter

All Implemented Interfaces:
Parameter
public class AgencyParameter
extends ListParameter

Parameter for Agencies

When rendered as a HTML input, it is displayed as a SELECT filled with agencies names, with also the option to select 'All agencies'. As all other ListParameter parameters, the option selected is then seen as a StringParameter.
